22
00:01:21,630 --> 00:01:23,550
Kotoko-san.

23
00:01:24,190 --> 00:01:27,410
Let's work hard on the rehabilitation together.

24
00:01:30,850 --> 00:01:33,430
Hey, Irie!

25
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:37,820
